OL,6,FITV Correspondent Tim Scott explains
OL,7,Fwhat led to the violent disorder that
OL,8,Fbroke out on 10 February 2023.
OL,10,FSeven men have been jailed for their
OL,11,Fpart in a riot outside a hotel in ,
OL,12,Fwhich was housing asylum seekers.
OL,14,FAn eighth man was given a suspended
OL,15,Fsentence.
OL,17,FDisorder broke out in on 10 February
OL,18,F2023 when around 300 people gathered
OL,19,Foutside the gates of the Suites Hotel.
