OL,6,FA police van was set on fire and
OL,7,Fmissiles were thrown at officers
OL,8,Ffacilitating an initially peaceful
OL,9,Fprotest which turned violent at the
OL,10,FSuites Hotel on Ribblers Lane.
OL,12,FPolice equipment including riot
OL,13,Fshields, helmets and metal bars were
OL,14,Falso taken from inside the van.
OL,16,FThree officers were injured, with two
OL,17,Fsustaining minor injuries and one
OL,18,FInspector requiring hospital treatment.
