OL,6,FAs part of extensive investigations
OL,7,Fofficers analysed over 150 pieces of
OL,8,Fbody worn video footage, 75 social
OL,9,Fmedia clips and four hours of drone
OL,10,Ffootage to prevent any further crime
OL,11,Fand bring those responsible to justice.
OL,13,FAt Liverpool Crown Court on Monday 18
OL,14,FMarch 2024, seven men were jailed for
OL,15,Fa total of over 18 years.
OL,17,FThe judge at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,18,Fsaid what happened brought shame on
OL,19,Fthe whole of Merseyside.
