OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News at the time, one
OL,7,Fof the asylum seekers staying at the
OL,8,Fhotel said they were scared: "they
OL,9,Fwere yelling and screaming, yes we
OL,10,Fwere frightened, especially when they
OL,11,Ftried to break the fence, maybe they
OL,12,Fcould set the whole hotel on fire"
OL,14,FMore than 80 thousand pounds worth of
OL,15,Fdamage was caused to the hotel.
