OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector John
OL,7,FFitzgerald said: " officers had
OL,8,Ffireworks fired at them from close
OL,9,Frange, bottles bricks and paving slabs
OL,10,Fwere thrown at them, but they remained
OL,11,Fprofessional and calm and restored
OL,12,Forder"
OL,14,FThe disturbance started after an
OL,15,Fallegation was made that an asylum
OL,16,Fseeker at the hotel had sexually
OL,17,Fassaulted a local girl, but from
OL,18,FMerseyside Police says no further
OL,19,Faction was taken after a thorough
OL,20,Finvestigation.
