OL,6,FBig Help Project is a Liverpool-based
OL,7,Fpoverty charity, who responded to the
OL,8,Fsentencing
OL,10,F"The way that residents at the Suites
OL,11,FHotel were treated, both at the time
OL,12,Fof the incident last year and in its
OL,13,Faftermath, is abhorrent.
OL,15,F"We hope that this sentencing can
OL,16,Ffinally draw a line under such a
OL,17,Fdisgraceful incident, allowing the
OL,18,Fsurrounding communities to live in
OL,19,Fpeace and charities to provide help
OL,20,Fwhere needed without obstacles."
